      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. This driver-focused example is equipped with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the Variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its sharp handling characteristics via Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and the weight-saving carbon fiber roof panel. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle body actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system operate within peak parameters. The suspension bushings and subframe mounts remain tight, offering a communicative steering feel that reflects its well-kept status.",
